4Geeks Academy offers a course called "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer" that prepares students for a career in data science and machine learning. The course is designed for beginners and covers topics such as Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and statistics. Students will learn to create predictive models using Python libraries like Pandas and Numpy, and explore algorithms such as Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. The course also focuses on supervised and unsupervised learning models. Students will have the opportunity to work on real-life cases and develop their own AI projects from development to deployment and maintenance. The course is 16 weeks long and includes three classes per week with a maximum class size of 12 students. Upon completion, students receive a certificate recognized by multiple organizations. No previous experience is required, and students can choose between English and Spanish for the syllabus and content. More information can be found at https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop